<div dir="ltr">Hi,<div>the default memheap size is 256MB, you can override it with oshrun -x SHMEM_SYMMETRIC_HEAP_SIZE=512M ... </div></div><div class="gmail_extra"><br><div class="gmail_quote">On Mon, Nov 17, 2014 at 3:38 PM, Timur Ismagilov <span dir="ltr">&lt;<a href="mailto:tismagilov@mail.ru" target="_blank">tismagilov@mail.ru</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br><blockquote class="gmail_quote" style="margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex">
